Long before I was forced to stay indoors, I spent most of my time ... indoors.
So, my fellow folks privileged enough to be able to work from home during this crisis, below are some picks that might make working from home more bearable.
You'll Need a Good Laptop or PCPhotograph: AppleWe're guessing you have a laptop or desktop of some kind, whether it's your own personal device or the one you brought from work.
If not, check out our Best Laptops, Best Cheap Laptops, and Best MacBooks guides.
If you're eyeing a desktop PC, we have recommendations for prebuilt gaming PCs that might be handy, or you can build your own for a lot less.